Package: phutil
Title: Persistence Homology Utilities
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Aymeric", "Stamm", , "aymeric.stamm@cnrs.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8725-3654")),
    person("Jason Cory", "Brunson", , "cornelioid@gmail.com", role = "ctb",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3126-9494"))
  )
Description: Implements a class for hosting persistence homology
    information in the form of a persistence diagram. The package also
    provides a set of functions to manipulate persistence diagrams, such
    as coercing them to different formats for compatibility with other
    packages or plotting them.
